These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
4 different pets are kept: turtle, snake, dog, frog
House: art-deco, gothic-revival, colonial, modern
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, colombian, indonesian, polish
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, nurse, electrician, security-guard
1. the colombian is the modern house##1
2. the indonesian is between the owner of the dog and the owner of the frog##2
3. the colombian is the fisherman##1
4. the security-guard is on the left of the fisherman##1
5. the art-deco house is on the left of the canadian##1
6. the electrician is the owner of the dog##1
7. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
8. the canadian is on the far right##1
9. the owner of the snake is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Pet   | snake | frog   | turtle  | dog  |
| House   | gothic-revival    | modern    | art-deco      | colonial    |
| Nationality   | polish | colombian | indonesian | canadian |
| Job     | security-guard  | fisherman       | nurse    | electrician     |

