.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, mirinda, soy-milk, tea
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, r&b, metal, rock
4 different pets are kept: bird, dog, frog, lizard
4 different games are played: scrabble, domino, whist, chess
1. the person playing chess is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
2. the person drinking juice is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the lizard is the person playing domino##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
5. the fan of rock is between the owner of the frog and the person playing scrabble##2
6. the person playing chess is between the fan of rock and the owner of the lizard##2
7. the owner of the bird is on the far right##1
8. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
9. the fan of metal is on the right of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage         | tea | mirinda    | soy-milk  | juice    |
| Music-Genre   | soul      | r&b  | rock  | metal |
| Pet           | lizard      | frog       | dog      | bird       |
| Game         | domino    | chess | whist | scrabble |

