.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, july, april, may
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, fishing, photography, traveling
4 different games are played: bridge, snooker, domino, poker
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, black, coral, yellow
1. the person playing domino is the person who likes black##1
2. the person who likes black is on the left of the person playing poker##1
3. the person who likes coral is on the left of the person who likes black##1
4. the person who likes black is on the left of the person who likes orange##1
5. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
6. the person playing snooker is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
7. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
8. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is traveling##2
9. the person who's hobby is photography is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person playing snooker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Birthday        | july | april     | february   | may     |
| Hobby       | fishing   | camping   | photography | traveling |
| Game         | bridge   | domino | poker       | snooker    |
| Color   | coral    | black | orange  | yellow    |

