.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, mechanic, police-officer, teacher
There 4 different types of food: onion, asparagus, pumpkin, kiwi
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, july, may, september
House: farmhouse, cape-cod, tower, victorian
 1. the person eating asparagus is on the far right##1
 2. the person eating kiwi is the fisherman##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the victorian house##1
 4. the farmhouse house is on the far left##1
 5. the person eating kiwi is the person who's birthday is in july##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
 7. the person eating asparagus is the police-officer##1
 8. the person eating onion is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
 9. the fisherman is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
10. the mechanic is between the person who's birthday is in february and the teacher##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Job           | fisherman  | teacher | mechanic     | police-officer |
| Food   | kiwi | onion  | pumpkin | asparagus       |
| Birthday           | july       | september    | may      | february           |
| House         | farmhouse | cape-cod   | victorian   | tower         |

