.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-5::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, garlic, lemon, peach
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, daisy, begonia, poppy
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, almond-milk, lemonade, tea
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, april, january, september
 1. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left##1
 3. the person who growsbegonia is the person eating garlic##1
 4. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 5. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person eating peach##1
 6. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 7. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
 8. the person who growsdaisy is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 9. the person eating lemon is between the person who's birthday is in september and the person drinking juice##2
10. the person drinking lemonade is the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Food          | garlic         | lemon         | asparagus     | peach      |
| Flower           | begonia | poppy | daffodil    | daisy     |
| Beverage   | juice      | lemonade       | tea    | almond-milk       |
| Birthday         | june     | january       | september | april |

