.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, freelancer, librarian, paramedic
House: colonial, wooden, futuristic, palace
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, bike, boat, jet-ski
City: hannover, miami, edinburgh, boston
1. the colonial house is between the person traveling to boston and the futuristic house##2
2. the freelancer is between the colonial house and the person driving the jet-ski##2
3. the person driving the boat is between the person traveling to miami and the person driving the bike##2
4. the librarian is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
5. the person driving the boat is the person driving the boat##1
6. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
7. the person driving the bike is on the left of the analyst##1
8. the futuristic house is on the far right##1
9. the wooden house is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Job           | librarian | freelancer | analyst  | paramedic |
| House   | wooden      | palace       | colonial     | futuristic      |
| Transport   | jet-ski   | bike      | boat   | helicopter   |
| City         | edinburgh   | boston    | hannover | miami   |

