4 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, bongani, vegafina, siglo
There 4 different types of food: pomegranate, garlic, cranberry, blueberry
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bike, subway, train
 1. the person driving the train is on the right of the game-smoker##1
 2. the person who likes lilac is the person eating cranberry##1
 3. the bongani-smoker is between the person eating cranberry and the person driving the subway##2
 4. the vegafina-smoker is the person driving the train##1
 5. the person eating blueberry is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
 6. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
 7. the person eating pomegranate is the person driving the airplane##1
 8. the siglo-smoker is on the far right##1
 9. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
10. the person eating cranberry is the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Color   | grey | lilac | aquamarine  | coral  |
| Cigar   | game       | vegafina   | bongani | siglo    |
| Food   | pomegranate   | cranberry   | blueberry | garlic |
| Transport     | airplane    | train   | bike    | subway  |

