The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officer, dressmaker, paramedic, manager
1. the person playing scrabble is between the paramedic and the police-officer##2
2. the paramedic is on the left of the fan of country##1
3. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
4. the police-officer is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
5. the dressmaker is between the paramedic and the person playing bridge##2
6. the fan of classical is the person playing billiard##1
7. the fan of country is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
8. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of reggae##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |      3      |   4    |
| Music-Genre      | classical  | country   | pop    | reggae  |
| Game   | billiard    | scrabble   | bridge | backgammon |
| Pet           | cat       | horse   | frog        | snake  |
| Job     | paramedic | dressmaker | police-officer         | manager |

