.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-9::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, bluemaster, bolivar, swisher
4 different games are played: chess, bridge, whist, go
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, house, indie, metal
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, writing, video-games, rock-climbing
 1. the bluemaster-smoker is the person playing whist##1
 2. the swisher-smoker is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 3. the person playing whist is the person who's hobby is writing##1
 4. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
 5. the fan of metal is the oliveros-smoker##1
 6. the fan of indie is on the far left##1
 7. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing whist##1
 8. the fan of house is on the far right##1
 9. the person playing chess is between the person playing go and the person who's hobby is collecting##2
10. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3      |     4     |
| Cigar          | swisher        | bolivar    | oliveros | bluemaster   |
| Game           | go | chess | bridge   | whist |
| Music-Genre   | indie         | folk       | metal      | house     |
| Hobby         | video-games       | rock-climbing | collecting    | writing  |

