 3. the cape-cod house is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
 4. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the palace house##1
 5. the owner of the goldfish is between the owner of the goat and the owner of the hamster##2
 6. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
 7. the chaman-smoker is the gothic-revival house##1
 8. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the hamster is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
10. the blend-smoker is the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
