 8. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
 9. the person who's sport is soccer is the fan of metal##1
10. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |     3      |    4     |
